      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Mesh convergence study performed on the pedicle screw shank and rod interface. Peak von Mises stress converged to within 3% between medium and fine meshes; fine mesh adopted for all production runs."
    },
