      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic continuum model with frictional contact at screw-rod interface. Simplifying assumptions (no plasticity, no fatigue damage) are appropriate for the static compression-bending scenario defined in F1717. Model form uncertainty quantified via ensemble spread."
