    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged; the overall evidence body is judged sufficient to support the Medium assurance level for the non-cannulated F1717 compression-bending scenario. Acceptance is conditional on the noted test-condition limitation being addressed in future validation cycles.",
